    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? This absolute gem is in showroom condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I've babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away and spotless. It drives like a dream and is just waiting for someone who will appreciate how pristine it truly is. Come take a look and see for yourself; you won't be disappointed!",
