    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example in pristine condition. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster with no evidence of stone chips, swirl marks, or scratches, having been protected by a professional ceramic coating and stored in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the leather seats remain taut and matte with no bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the smallest interior light, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It drives tight and quiet, reflecting its low-mileage and pampered history. The sale includes all original owner\u2019s manuals, two sets of keys, and a folder of maintenance receipts. This is, without question, one of the finest examples available on the market today.",
      "price": 46500.0,
