    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccably maintained 996.2 Carrera 4S, featuring the iconic wide-body architecture and integrated rear reflector strip. This example boasts the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six engine with a documented IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement for peace of mind. Power is delivered via a precise six-speed manual transaxle to an advanced viscous-clutch all-wheel-drive system. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, benefitting from factory-spec Bilstein dampers and four-piston monobloc calipers paired with cross-drilled rotors. The finish shows no signs of oxidation, and the cabin remains free of bolster wear or switchgear delamination. A turn-key performance icon for the discerning collector.",
